\id 1PE
\h 1 Pegr
\toc3 1Pe.
\toc2 1 Pegr
\toc1 Tnejil Tuꞌj Pegr
\mt1 Tnejil Tuꞌj Pegr
\ip Pegr tbꞌi jun tsanjil Jesús, a kubꞌ tzꞌibꞌin te uꞌj lo, a xi smaꞌn kye nimil kysipin kyibꞌ toj txꞌotxꞌ te Asia Menor, quꞌn otaq chi okx toj joybꞌil ex yajbꞌil noq tuꞌn tpajjo kynimbꞌil. Nimxix nqꞌuqbꞌin Pegr kykꞌuꞌjjo nimil, ex ntzaj tnaꞌn kye tzeꞌn ẍi klete tuꞌn Dios; exsin tzaj tqꞌoꞌn jun qꞌuqꞌbꞌil kykꞌuꞌj noq tuꞌnjo tkyimlin ex tjawlintz anqꞌin Crist. Ex atzin qꞌuqbꞌil kykꞌuꞌjjo, a tulil qAjaw tkabꞌ majin qꞌilkye, tuꞌn kyxiꞌ toj kyaꞌj najal tukꞌa te jun majx. Ayetzin nimil luꞌn, quꞌn n-ikyꞌx yajbꞌil kyuꞌn noq tuꞌn tpaj Jesucrist, ex at kyoklin tiꞌjjo tqoptzꞌajiyil, aj tul juntl majl (\xt 4:13; 5:1\xt*).
\ip Toj tkyaqiljo yol tojjo uꞌj luꞌn, ntzaj t-xnaqꞌtzin Pegr, tuꞌn t-xi qiꞌn jun qchwinqil tbꞌanil tuꞌn tok te jun yekbꞌil kywutz txqantl, tzeꞌnkuxjo tbꞌanil txokbꞌil ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Dios qe. Ayetzin nimil bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tkyij kytzaqpiꞌn a jniꞌ nkubꞌ kybꞌinchin nya wen, tej naꞌmxtaq kynimin tiꞌj qAjaw; exsin kxel kyiꞌntz jun kychwinqil saqxix wen, tuꞌntzintla ntiꞌ jun yolbꞌil kyiꞌj kyuꞌnxjal nya nimil. Ex nxi tqꞌoꞌn Pegr tumil kye junjun chꞌuq xjal toj Ttanim Dios, a tzeꞌnku kye aqꞌnil, ex kye chmilbꞌaj, ex kye tij xjal ex kye kuꞌxin. Ex at juntl tumil, qa wen tuꞌn kykubꞌ qnimin aj kawil. Tibꞌaj tkyaqiljo lo, ntzaj tnaꞌn tuꞌn tkubꞌ qbꞌinchin tkyaqil tukꞌa qkꞌuꞌjbꞌil qxol.
\c 1
\s1 Jun qꞌolbꞌil tuꞌn Pegr
\p 
\v 1 Ayiꞌn Pegr jun tsanjil Jesucrist;\x + \xo 1:1\xt Mt. 4:18; Mr. 1:16; Lc. 5:1-11.\x* nxi ntzꞌibꞌinjiꞌy uꞌj luꞌn kyeꞌy, a ayiꞌy kysipin kyibꞌa tuꞌn tpaj kynimbꞌila,\x + \xo 1:1\xt Sant. 1:1.\x* ex ma chi oka te bꞌetin xjal toj txꞌotxꞌ te Ponto, Galacia, Capadocia, Asia ex Bitinia.
\v 2 Ayiꞌy o chi jaw skꞌoꞌn tuꞌn qMan Dios, a tzeꞌnkuxjo t-xim attaq te tnejil, noq tuꞌn kysaqixa tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, tuꞌntzintla tkubꞌ kynimiꞌn, ex tuꞌn kyoka tzꞌaqle tuꞌn tchkyꞌel Jesucrist. Noqit nim t-xtalbꞌil ex tnukꞌbꞌil kyibꞌaja toj tkyaqil.
\s1 Ajo t-xilin kolbꞌil
\p 
\v 3 Qo nimsin tbꞌi tDios ex tTata qAjaw Jesucrist, quꞌn noq tuꞌn tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil tkꞌuꞌj, tzaj tqꞌoꞌn tumil tuꞌn qitzꞌje tkabꞌ majin, noq tuꞌn tjawlintz anqꞌin Jesucrist kyxol kyimnin.\x + \xo 1:3\xt Jn. 3:3-7; Ro. 6:4-13.\x* A tzaj qꞌoꞌnte nim qꞌuqbꞌil qkꞌuꞌjjo toj qchwinqil tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ,
\v 4 ex a ktzajil qꞌoꞌnte jun qetzbꞌil te jun majx, a kꞌuꞌn tuꞌn Dios toj kyaꞌj, tuꞌntzintla mi xitje, ex tuꞌn mi yaje, ex tuꞌn mi molje.
\v 5 Ex noq tuꞌn kynimbꞌila tiꞌj Dios, aku Dios nklon kyeꞌy tukꞌa tkyaqil tipin, tuꞌntzintla tlajetjo kolbꞌil, a bꞌantnin tuꞌn, ex ktzajil tyekꞌin, aj tpon bꞌaj tqꞌijil.
\p 
\v 6 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, nimx nchi tzalaja, exla qa il tiꞌj tuꞌn tikyꞌx yajbꞌil kyuꞌn toj jteꞌbꞌin qꞌij.
\v 7 Ajo n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn jaꞌlin, tzeꞌnku jun qꞌaqꞌ te saqsbꞌil kynimbꞌila, ikyxjo tzeꞌnku qꞌanpwaq il tiꞌj tuꞌn tsaqix tuꞌn qꞌaqꞌ. Me atzin kyinimbꞌila nimxixtl toklin tzeꞌnku qꞌanpwaq, quꞌn atzin qꞌanpwaq knajil, me atzin kynimbꞌila kyjel teꞌ te jun majx. Ikytzin kyejiꞌy kynimbꞌil tzeꞌnku te qꞌanpwaq, aj tsaqix tuꞌn qꞌaqꞌ; qa ma chi weꞌy toj tkyaqiljo n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn, axte Dios k-yolil wen kyiꞌja, ex kjawil tnimsin kybꞌiy, ex ktzajil tqꞌoꞌn nim kyokliꞌn, aj tul Jesucrist juntl maj.
\v 8 Exla qa naꞌm kylontiy, me ma qe kykꞌuꞌja tiꞌj; exla qa ntiꞌ tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ tuꞌn kykaꞌyiꞌn tiꞌj jaꞌlin, me at kynimbꞌila tiꞌj,\x + \xo 1:8\xt Jn. 20:29.\x* ex nim nchi tzalaja tukꞌa jun t-xilin tzaljbꞌil, a ntiꞌ tumil tuꞌn tbꞌant kyqꞌmaꞌntey tkyaqil,
\v 9 quꞌn nkykꞌmoꞌnjiꞌy ajo t-xilin kynimbꞌila, a kolbꞌil te jun majx.
\p 
\v 10 Kyojjo qꞌij ojtxe, aye yolil Tyol Dios, aye i kꞌmoꞌnte Tyol, nim i xpichꞌin tiꞌj, ex i jyoꞌn tiꞌjjo t-xilin kolbꞌil, a tuꞌntaq xi tqꞌoꞌn Dios kyeꞌy tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil.
\v 11 Nimx i xpichꞌin tiꞌj, tuꞌn tel kynikyꞌ te, ankye ex jtojtzin bꞌajjo a otaq tzaj tqꞌmaꞌn T-xew Crist, a Xewbꞌaj Xjan, toj kyanmin, tej t-xi tqꞌmaꞌn qa iltaq tiꞌj tuꞌn tikyꞌx yajbꞌil tuꞌn Crist, ex yajxi tuꞌn tjaw nimsit tbꞌi, tbꞌajlinxiꞌ yajlajtz.
\v 12 Me mix kanine kynabꞌl tuꞌn tel kynikyꞌ tiꞌjjo t-xilin lo, quꞌn tzaj tqꞌmaꞌn Dios kye, qa nya te kyex nchi ajbꞌinetaq toj kyaqꞌin, qalaꞌ te qe jaꞌlin, quꞌn i yolin tiꞌj a naꞌmtaq tel kynikyꞌ tiꞌj. Me atzin jaꞌlin, ayetzin kyeꞌ ma tzꞌel kynikyꞌa tiꞌj, kyuꞌnjo aye nchi yolin tiꞌjjo Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, noq tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, a tzaj smaꞌn toj kyaꞌj. Nimxix t-xilinjo lo; majqexpe kye angel kyaj tuꞌn tel kynikyꞌ te.
\s1 Jun txokbꞌil tuꞌn Dios tuꞌn qok xjanxix toj tkyaqil
\p 
\v 13 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kyximinkuxixsiꞌn wen alkye kꞌwel kybꞌinchiꞌn. Kytzyumtzin kyibꞌa, ex kyinxsin jun kychwinqila tzꞌaqle. Qexsin kykꞌuꞌja tiꞌjjo a ktzajil tqꞌoꞌn Dios tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil, aj tul Jesucrist juntl maj.
\v 14 Kyniminkuy Dios tzeꞌnqeku kꞌwal te kytata: Mi txi kyqꞌoꞌn kyibꞌa tojjo kyachbꞌila, a attaq, tej naꞌmtaq tel kynikyꞌa te Dios.
\v 15 Qalaꞌ, chi bꞌet-xixa toj jun tumil xjanxix toj kychwinqila, quꞌn ate Dios, a xtxkon kyeꞌy, tuꞌn kyxi lipeꞌy tiꞌj, xjanxix teꞌ.
\v 16 Ikytziꞌn tzeꞌnku ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios: Chi okxa xjan, quꞌn xjanqin weꞌch.\x + \xo 1:16\xt Lv. 11:44-45; 19:2.\x*
\p 
\v 17 Ex qa ma tzꞌok kyqꞌoꞌn Dios te kyMaꞌn, kynaꞌntziꞌn qa kchi okilxjal toj xjelbꞌil tuꞌn, a mi n-ok tkaꞌyin kytenxjal, qalaꞌ kkawil jikyinxix wen. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, chi bꞌettzintza toj tchewil Dios tkyaqil qꞌij, quꞌn ma chi oka te jun bꞌetin xjal tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, noq tuꞌn tpaj kynimbꞌila tiꞌj Crist.
\v 18 Quꞌn ate Dios ma klon kyeꞌy tojjo kychwinqila, a ntiꞌtaq tajbꞌin, a tzeꞌnku tzaj kyyekꞌin ojtxe kyxeꞌchila. Quꞌn bꞌiꞌnxix kyuꞌn, qa a chojbꞌil tejo kolbꞌil mix chjete tukꞌa jun tiꞌ, a kbꞌajil, tzeꞌnku qꞌanpwaq mo saqpwaq;
\v 19 qalaꞌ tukꞌa tchkyꞌel Crist, a tbꞌanilxix te jun majx, a xi qꞌoyit te chojbꞌil qil twutz Dios, tzeꞌnku jun tal tal rit te oyaj twutz qMan, a tzꞌaqle, ex ntiꞌ tkyꞌi.
\v 20 Quꞌn ate Crist jaw tskꞌoꞌn Dios, tuꞌn tok te chojbꞌil qil, a naꞌmxtaq tkubꞌ tbꞌinchin tkyaqil tchꞌiysbꞌin. Me tzmax tzaluꞌn, a chꞌix tjapin bꞌaj tqꞌijil, ma kubꞌ tyekꞌin tibꞌ, noq tuꞌn kyel wena.
\v 21 Quꞌn noq tuꞌn Crist, o chi nimiꞌn tiꞌj Dios, a jatz anqꞌin kyxol kyimnin, ex ma jaw nimsin tuꞌn Dios, tuꞌntzintla ajo kynimbꞌila ex qꞌuqbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja tuꞌn tten tiꞌj Dios.
\p 
\v 22 Atzin jaꞌlin, noq tuꞌn ma kubꞌ kyniminjiꞌy Tbꞌanil Tqanil, ma chi saqixa tuꞌn, tuꞌntzintla ttenxix kykꞌuꞌja kyiꞌj txqantl nimil. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kykꞌuꞌjlimtzin kyibꞌtza nimxix jun tukꞌa juntl, tukꞌa tkyaqil kyanmiꞌn.
\v 23 Quꞌn ma chi itzꞌjiꞌy tkabꞌ majin, nya tuꞌn jun kytatiy tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, a kkyimil; qalaꞌ tuꞌn Tyol Dios, a itzꞌ, ex ktenbꞌil te jun majx.\x + \xo 1:23\xt Jn. 3:3-7; Sant. 1:18; 1Pe. 1:3.\x*
\v 24 Quꞌn ikytzin ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios:
\q1 Tkyaqilxjal ikyxjo tzeꞌnku tal kꞌul.
\q1 Ex ajo kybꞌinchbꞌin ikyxjo tzeꞌnku t-xmakil kꞌul.
\q1 Quꞌn atzin te kꞌul ktzqijil,
\q1 ex atzin t-xmakil k-elil tzꞌaq.
\q1 
\v 25 Me metzin teꞌ Tyol qAjaw ktenbꞌil teꞌ te jun majx.\x + \xo 1:25\xt Is. 40:6-8.\x*
\p Ex atzin yol lo, a Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, a nyolajtz kyxola.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kytzaqpinkjtzinjiꞌy tkyaqiljo nya bꞌaꞌn, ex jniꞌ sbꞌuꞌbꞌl, junx tukꞌa xmiletzꞌil, exsin loꞌchj kꞌuꞌjbꞌaj ex tkyaqil iqj yol.
\v 2 Ex chi okxa tzeꞌnku jun neꞌẍ n-oqꞌ tiꞌj tmiꞌẍ, tuꞌn tchꞌiy. Ikytzintla kyejiꞌy kyjyomtzinjiꞌy Tyol Dios, a tzꞌaqle, tuꞌntzintla kychꞌiya tiꞌjjo t-xilin kolbꞌil,
\v 3 quꞌn ma kynikyꞌbꞌiy qa ate qAjaw tbꞌanilxix.\x + \xo 2:3\xt Sal. 34:8.\x*
\s1 Jesús, a Abꞌj itzꞌxix, tuꞌn tchꞌiy Ttanim tibꞌaj
\p 
\v 4 Chi laqꞌetza tkꞌatz qAjaw, a Abꞌj itzꞌxix, a s-el kyiꞌjlinxjal, nyakuj ntiꞌ tajbꞌin toj kywutz, me tbꞌanilx twutz qMan Dios, ex skꞌoꞌnxix tuꞌn.
\v 5 Ikyqetzin kyejiꞌy tzeꞌnku abꞌj itzꞌ, kyjaꞌ kyjaw chꞌiysiꞌn tuꞌn kyoka te tja qMan, a bꞌinchin tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan; ex tuꞌn kyoka te jun chꞌuq pale xjanxix, tuꞌn kyxi kyqꞌoꞌn oyaj tukꞌa tkyaqil kyanmiꞌn, a ntzalaj qMan Dios kyiꞌj, noq tuꞌn Jesucrist.
\v 6 Quꞌn ikytziꞌn ntqꞌmaꞌn Dios toj Tuꞌjil Tyol kyjaluꞌn:
\q1 Kꞌwel nqꞌonjiꞌy Abꞌj toj tnam Sion,
\q2 a nimxix toklin te tqꞌuqiljo ja.
\q1 Atzin Abꞌj lo, skꞌoꞌnxix wuꞌn ex tbꞌanilxix.
\q1 Alkyejo knimil tiꞌj, nlay tzꞌel toj txꞌixewch.\x + \xo 2:6\xt Is. 28:16.\x*
\p 
\v 7 Atzin jaꞌlin, ayiꞌy, a ma chi nimiꞌn tiꞌj, atzin Abꞌjjo tbꞌanilxix, me ankye qe, a mi chi nimin tiꞌj, kchi okil tzeꞌnku ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios:
\q1 Atzin Abꞌj, a s-el kyiꞌjlin bꞌinchil ja, ma tzꞌok te nimxix toklin te tqꞌuqil tẍkyin,\x + \xo 2:7\xt Sal. 118:22.\x*
\q1 
\v 8 ex ma tzꞌok te jun Abꞌj te toljsbꞌil, ex tuꞌn kyjaw takpajxjal tiꞌj.\x + \xo 2:8\xt Is. 8:14-15.\x*
\p Ex kchi jawil toljxjal tiꞌj, tzeꞌnku t-xim Dios, quꞌn mi xi kynimin Tbꞌanil Tqanil.
\s1 Aye nimil etzinqe tuꞌn qMan Dios
\p 
\v 9 Me metzin kyeꞌ ma chi oka te jun tyajil skꞌoꞌnxix tuꞌn Dios, a Nmaq Kawil toj kyaꞌj, ex te pale tuꞌn tajbꞌin te, ex te jun chꞌuq xjal xjanxix,\x + \xo 2:9\xt Ex. 19:5-6.\x* ex te jun tnam, a teku Dios,\x + \xo 2:9\xt Deu. 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 26:18; Tit. 2:14.\x* tuꞌntzintla t-xi kyqꞌmaꞌnjiꞌy a tbꞌanil t-xilin Dios,\x + \xo 2:9\xt Is. 43:21.\x* a xtxkon kyeꞌy tuꞌn kyetza tojjo tqxopinil il, tuꞌn kyokxa tojjo tspikyꞌemil te jun majx.\x + \xo 2:9\xt Is. 9:2.\x*
\v 10 Quꞌn ojtxe, ntiꞌtaq kymujbꞌil kyibꞌa, me atzin jaꞌlin, ma chi oka te Ttanim Dios. Ex ojtxe, naꞌmtaq tuꞌn tyekꞌin te Dios tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil tkꞌuꞌj kyiꞌja, me atzin jaꞌlin ma tzaj qꞌaqꞌin tkꞌuꞌj kyiꞌja.\x + \xo 2:10\xt Os. 2:23.\x*
\s1 Chi bꞌet-xixa toj tumil, tuꞌn kyajbꞌiꞌn te Dios
\p 
\v 11 Ayiꞌy werman, nimx nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja, ayiꞌy nyakuj bꞌetin xjalqiꞌy tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ. Nchin kubꞌsin nwutza kyeꞌy, tuꞌn tkubꞌ kytzyuꞌn kyibꞌa tiꞌjjo kyachbꞌila, a nya wen, a nchi qꞌojin tiꞌj kyanmiꞌn.
\v 12 Ex chi bꞌet-xa toj tumil kyxoljo nya nimil. Ikytziꞌn, exla qa nchi yolbꞌin kyiꞌja, a nyakuj aj ilqiꞌy, me k-okil kykaꞌyin ajo kybꞌinchbꞌiꞌn wen, ex kchi nimsil tbꞌi qMan Dios, aj tpon qꞌij tuꞌn kynimin.
\p 
\v 13 Kyniminqekujiꞌy tkyaqil kawbꞌil tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, quꞌn tuꞌn nimilqiꞌy; tzeꞌnku te nmaq kawil, noq tuꞌn toklin nimxix,
\v 14 ex ikyxjo kye aj kawil, a smaꞌnqe tuꞌn, tuꞌn kykubꞌ kawitjo bꞌinchil il, ex tuꞌn kyyolin wen kyiꞌjjo aye nchi bꞌinchin bꞌaꞌn.
\v 15 Quꞌn ate Dios taj tuꞌn tkubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy wen, tuꞌntzintla mi chi kybꞌinxjal kyyoljo, a nchi yolbꞌin kyiꞌja, ayeꞌ ntiꞌ kynabꞌl, ex ntiꞌ tumil kyyol.
\v 16 Quꞌn tzaqpinqiꞌy tjaqꞌ kawbꞌil tuꞌn kybꞌinchiꞌn tzeꞌnku kyaja, me mi tzꞌajbꞌiꞌn tzaqbꞌibꞌl luꞌn kyuꞌn, tuꞌn kybꞌinchiꞌn il; qalaꞌ chi anqꞌiꞌn tzeꞌnku jun taqꞌnil qMan Dios.
\v 17 Kyqꞌonxsiꞌn nimbꞌil te tkyaqil. Kꞌuꞌjlinqekjiꞌy jniꞌ nimil. Tenxit tchewil Dios kyiꞌja. Ex kyniminkujiꞌy nmaq kawil.
\s1 Bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tikyꞌx yajbꞌil quꞌn tzeꞌnku te Crist
\p 
\v 18 Ayiꞌy aqꞌnil, kyniminkutzinjiꞌy tajaw aqꞌuntl, nya noq oꞌkxjo kye wenqe kyeꞌy, ex tbꞌanilqex toj kywutza, qalaꞌ ikyxjo kye, a kujqe.
\v 19 Quꞌn wenxix teꞌ twutz Dios, qa ma tzikyꞌx yajbꞌil kyuꞌn, a nya toj tumil, noq tuꞌn nimilqiꞌy tiꞌj Dios.
\v 20 Me qatzin qa ma kubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy nya wen, exsin qa ma chi ok laqtziꞌn tuꞌn tpajjo lo, ¿Ma okpela chi ela wena twutz Dios tuꞌn tikyꞌx kyuꞌn? Me qa chebꞌe nkubꞌ kypaꞌnjiꞌy yajbꞌil, noq tuꞌn kybꞌinchinjiꞌy wen, axixpente wenjo twutz qMan Dios.
\v 21 Quꞌn tuꞌnpetziꞌn, ma qo tzaj ttxkoꞌn Dios tuꞌn tikyꞌx quꞌn, tzeꞌnku te Crist nim ma tzikyꞌx tuꞌn, noq tuꞌn qpaj; ex tuꞌnjo lo, ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn jun yekꞌbꞌil qe.
\v 22 Quꞌn ntiꞌx jun til kubꞌ tbꞌinchin, ex mix jun maj kubꞌ tsbꞌuꞌn jun aꞌla.\x + \xo 2:22\xt Is. 53:9.\x*
\v 23 Ex tej s-ok yisoꞌn, ex mi s-aj ttzaqꞌwin tukꞌa yasbꞌil; ex tej s-ikyꞌx jniꞌ yajbꞌil tuꞌn, mi xqanbꞌin kyiꞌjxjal; qalaꞌ noq xi toqxenin tibꞌ te Dios, a Kawil tzꞌaqle tibꞌaj tkyaqil.
\v 24 Ate Crist xi iqin teꞌ jniꞌ qil tuꞌnjo t-xmilil, tej tkyim twutz cruz, tuꞌntzintla qkyimqe tiꞌj tkyaqiljo il, ex tuꞌn qanqꞌin toj jun chwinqil tzꞌaqle. Quꞌn tuꞌn tkyꞌixjlbꞌin, ex tuꞌn tkyimlin twutz cruz, ma qo qꞌanit.\x + \xo 2:24\xt Is. 53:5.\x*
\v 25 Ayetzin kye nchi bꞌettaqa ojtxe tzeꞌnqeku rit ma chi kyij naj.\x + \xo 2:25\xt Is. 53:6.\x* Me atzin jaꞌlin, ma chi ul meltzꞌaja tukꞌa Crist, a Kyikꞌlel kyeꞌy, ex Kaꞌyil tiꞌj kyanmiꞌn.
\c 3
\s1 Jun tumil kyejo mejebꞌlin
\p 
\v 1 Ex ikyx kyejiꞌy xuꞌjlbꞌaj, kyniminkujiꞌy kychmila,\x + \xo 3:1\xt Ef. 5:22; Col. 3:18.\x* tuꞌntzintla qa at jun n-el tiꞌjlin Tyol Dios, aku kubꞌ tiꞌj tnabꞌl, nya tukꞌa jun yol, qalaꞌ noq tuꞌnjo wen nbꞌant tuꞌn,
\v 2 aj tok tkaꞌyin chmilbꞌaj, qa nbꞌet t-xuꞌjil tukꞌa junchꞌin tumil ex tukꞌa nim tnimbꞌil te.
\v 3 Ex ajo kybꞌinchbꞌin kyibꞌa, nya oꞌkxjo tuꞌn tqꞌanchaꞌlix, tzeꞌnku tuꞌn tbꞌaj kyxyebꞌin kywiꞌy, noq tuꞌn kyyekꞌin kyibꞌa, ex tuꞌn tokx kyqꞌoꞌn kyuꞌy te qꞌanpwaq, ex kyxbꞌaliꞌn wiyilxix, noq tuꞌn kyel wena kywutzxjal.\x + \xo 3:3\xt 1Tim. 2:9.\x*
\v 4 Qalaꞌ atzin kybꞌinchbꞌin kyibꞌa, tuꞌn tyekꞌin t-xilin kyanmiꞌn, ajo tbꞌanilx tuꞌn mi naje, tzeꞌnku jun kyanmiꞌn bꞌunin ex wenxix, a tbꞌanilxix twutz qMan Dios.
\v 5 Quꞌn ikytziꞌn kyojjo qꞌij ojtxe, ikytzin ẍi bꞌinchine kyibꞌjo xuꞌjlbꞌaj, ayeꞌ xjanqexix twutz Dios, ex ma qe kykꞌuꞌj twutz. Ex ma kubꞌ kynimin kychmil,
\v 6 ikytziꞌn tzeꞌnku te Sara, kubꞌ tnimin Abraham, ex xi tqꞌoꞌn toklin te tnejil.\x + \xo 3:6\xt Gen. 18:12.\x* Atzin jaꞌlin, ayetzin kyeꞌ, ma chi oka te tal Sara, qa ma kubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy wen, ex qa mi xi kyqꞌon kyibꞌa toj xobꞌajil twutz txꞌotxꞌ.
\p 
\v 7 Ex ikyxjo kyeꞌ chmilbꞌaj, tenxit kynabꞌla kyukꞌa kyxuꞌjila, ex kyqꞌonktziꞌn kyoklin,\x + \xo 3:7\xt Ef. 5:25; Col. 3:19.\x* quꞌn ntiꞌxix kyipin tzeꞌnku kye ichin, ex at kyoklin junx kyukꞌiy twutz qMan, tiꞌjjo akꞌaj chwinqil, noq tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil Dios. Kybꞌinchinkujiꞌy lo, tuꞌn ntiꞌ jun tiꞌ aku tzꞌok miyoꞌnte kynaꞌj Diosa.
\s1 Ayejo n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn, noq tuꞌn tpajjo wen
\p 
\v 8 Atzin jaꞌlin, noq tuꞌn tjapin bꞌaj nyola, kxel nqꞌmaꞌn tuꞌn kymujbꞌin te kyibꞌa kyxolxa tukꞌa tzaljbꞌil, ex tukꞌa tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja. Tenxit kykꞌuꞌja kyxolxa nyakuj kyitzꞌin kyibꞌa. Kymojim kyibꞌa kyxolxa tukꞌa kymutxbꞌil kyibꞌa.
\v 9 Qa ma tzꞌok bꞌinchin jun nya wen mo jun yasbꞌil kyiꞌja, mi tzaj kymeltzꞌiꞌn tukꞌa juntl nya wen mo juntl yasbꞌil te t-xel. Qalaꞌ, bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn t-xi kyqaniꞌn tkyꞌiwbꞌil Dios kyibꞌajjo nchi bꞌinchin mibꞌin kyiꞌja, quꞌn ikyxjo kyeꞌ, ma chi txoklajtza tuꞌn kykꞌmontejiꞌy tkyꞌiwbꞌil qMan Dios.
\v 10 Quꞌn ikytziꞌn ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios:
\q1 Ankye teꞌ taj tuꞌn ttzalaj toj tchwinqil,
\q1 ex tuꞌn tten tkyaqil qꞌij toj ttxutxjil,
\q1 il tiꞌj tuꞌn tjkꞌunte taqꞌ, tuꞌn mi yoline nya bꞌaꞌn,
\q1 ex tuꞌn mi sbꞌuꞌne kyiꞌjxjal tuꞌn ttzi.
\q1 
\v 11 Bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tel tpaꞌn tibꞌ tiꞌjjo nya bꞌaꞌn,
\q2 tuꞌn tkubꞌ bꞌinchitjo wen, ex tuꞌn tok tilil tuꞌn, tuꞌn tknetjo nukꞌbꞌil toj tchwinqil, ex tuꞌn tok lipe tiꞌj.
\q1 
\v 12 Quꞌn axte qAjaw nkaꞌyin kye, a tzꞌaqleqe, ex nkubꞌ tbꞌiꞌn kynaꞌj Dios.
\q1 Me ayetzin kye nchi bꞌinchin nya bꞌaꞌn, nqꞌojle qAjaw kyiꞌj.\x + \xo 3:12\xt Sal. 34:12-16.\x*
\p 
\v 13 ¿Ma atpela jun aku tzꞌok bꞌinchin te jun nya bꞌaꞌn kyiꞌja, qa kukx tok tililjo kyuꞌn, tuꞌn tkubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy wen?
\v 14 Exla qa ma tzikyꞌx yajbꞌil kyuꞌn, noq tuꞌnjo kychwinqila tzꞌaqle, me kyꞌiwlinqexixa tuꞌn qMan Dios.\x + \xo 3:14\xt Mt. 5:10.\x* Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, mi chi xobꞌa te jun aꞌla, ex mi ja naj kynabꞌla.
\v 15 Qalaꞌ kynimsinksa tbꞌi Crist toj kyanmiꞌn, a kyAjawa, tuꞌntzintla bꞌantnin kyteꞌn, tuꞌn t-xi kytzaqꞌwiꞌn tkyaqiljo nchi kanin qanilte tiꞌjjo qꞌuqbꞌil kykꞌuꞌja at.\x + \xo 3:15\xt Col. 4:6; Eb. 3:6.\x*
\v 16 Me kytzaqꞌwinxa tukꞌa jun yol bꞌunin ex tukꞌa jun kymutxbꞌil kyibꞌa. Chi bꞌet-xa toj tumil, tzeꞌnkuxjo ntqꞌmaꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan toj kyanmiꞌn, tuꞌntzintla ttzaj kytxꞌixewjo nchi yolbꞌin kyiꞌja, noq tuꞌn tpajjo nimilqiꞌy tiꞌj Crist.
\v 17 Quꞌn tbꞌanilx teꞌ, tuꞌn tikyꞌx quꞌn, noq tuꞌn qbꞌinchbꞌin wen, qa iky taj Diosjo, ex nya tuꞌn qbꞌinchbꞌin nya bꞌaꞌn.
\v 18 Quꞌn aku te Crist tzꞌaqlexix, ex ikyꞌx kyimin tuꞌn, noq jun maj tuꞌn tpajjo qil, awo nya bꞌaꞌnqo, ex tuꞌn qpon tiꞌn tkꞌatz Dios. Twutzxix teꞌ qa ma kyim t-xmilil, me atzin jaꞌlin, itzꞌ noq tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan.
\v 19 Ex tuꞌnjo Xewbꞌaj Xjan, bꞌeꞌx xiꞌ yolil Tbꞌanil Tqanil kyejo kyimnin jpuꞌnqekx tojjo kynajbꞌil kyimnin,
\v 20 ayeꞌ mi kubꞌ kynimin Tyol Dios ojtxe kyojjo qꞌij, tej tzmataq nbꞌinchin Noé tiꞌj arka, exla qa chebꞌetaq n-ayoꞌn Dios kyiꞌj tuꞌn tajtz tiꞌj kyanmin. Me mix i nimine; qalaꞌ oꞌkxjo wajxaq kybꞌaj i klet toj aꞌ.\x + \xo 3:20\xt Gen. 6:1—7:24.\x*
\v 21 Me atzin aꞌ jun t-xilin yekꞌbꞌil te qe jaꞌlin tuꞌnjo jawsbꞌil aꞌ. Quꞌn ma qo klet tuꞌnjo txꞌajbꞌil qanmin tuꞌn Dios, ex nya noq tuꞌn tel chꞌin tzꞌil tiꞌj qxmilil tuꞌn jun jawsbꞌil aꞌ toj aꞌ. Quꞌn atzinjo jawsbꞌil aꞌ lo, jun techil qa o txjetjo qanmin twutz Dios noq tuꞌn tjawlintz anqꞌin Jesucrist kyxol kyimnin,
\v 22 a o japin toj kyaꞌj kawil tukꞌa qMan Dios tibꞌaj tkyaqil angel, jniꞌ kawil, ex tkyaqil at kyipin, tuꞌntzintla tkubꞌ kynimin.
\c 4
\s1 Qo bꞌet tzeꞌnkuxjo taj Dios
\p 
\v 1 Quꞌn ikytziꞌn tzeꞌnku te Crist, ma tzikyꞌx tuꞌn toj t-xmilil, exsin ikyx kyejiꞌy bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn t-xi kyqꞌoꞌn kyibꞌa tuꞌn tikyꞌx yajbꞌil kyuꞌn, noq tuꞌn tpaj kynimbꞌila. Quꞌn alkyeꞌ ma tzikyꞌx tuꞌn toj t-xmilil, tok tilil tuꞌn, tuꞌn tkyij ttzaqpiꞌn il,
\v 2 tuꞌntzintla mi bꞌete tojjo chꞌintl tchwinqil tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ, a tzeꞌnkuxjo tajbꞌil kyachbꞌilxjal; qalaꞌ tzeꞌnkuxitlaꞌ tajbꞌil Dios tukꞌa.
\v 3 Akuxjo jaꞌlin, a nkubꞌ kybꞌinchintaqa ojtxe, a tzeꞌnkuxjo kytzeqbꞌilxjal nya nimilqe. Quꞌn ikytaqtzin nchi bꞌetejiꞌy tojjo jniꞌ nya wen, ex nimkutaq n-el kyanmiꞌn tiꞌj, ex txꞌujtinelqiꞌy, ex manyor kyꞌaꞌjilqiꞌy, ex noqx nchex lipe tiꞌj tkyaqiljo il, ex nchi kꞌuliꞌn kywutzjo kywutzbꞌiyil junxil kydiosxjal.
\v 4 Me atzin jaꞌlin, nya wen n-ele toj kywutzxjal, tuꞌn mi nchi bꞌettla toj kyachbꞌil junx kyukꞌa. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, nchi yolbꞌin nya wen kyiꞌja.
\v 5 Me nya yajku kchi okil toj paꞌbꞌin twutzjo Dios, a Kawil kyibꞌajjo tkyaqil kyimnin, ex aye itzꞌqextaq.
\v 6 Quꞌn ayetziꞌn, a o chi kyim, ma yolajtz Tbꞌanil Tqanil kye, tuꞌntzintla tanqꞌin kyanmin tuꞌn Dios, exla qa ma kubꞌ kyximinxjal qa ntiꞌ kyoklin tuꞌn kyanqꞌin tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ; ex bꞌeꞌx i kubꞌ kybꞌyoꞌn.
\p 
\v 7 Quꞌn chꞌix tuꞌn tjapin bꞌaj tqꞌijil tzaluꞌn twutz txꞌotxꞌ; tuꞌnpetziꞌn, tenxix kynabꞌla, ex kytzyumtzin kyibꞌa, tuꞌn kyokxa toj naꞌj Dios.
\v 8 Me tibꞌaj tkyaqiljo lo, axix il tiꞌjjo kykꞌuꞌjbꞌil kyibꞌa, quꞌn atzin kykꞌuꞌjbꞌil kyibꞌa, knajsitil nim il tuꞌn.\x + \xo 4:8\xt Pr. 10:12; 1Co. 13:7.\x*
\v 9 Kykꞌmomtzin kyibꞌa toj kyjay jun tukꞌa juntl,\x + \xo 4:9\xt Ro. 12:13.\x* ex mi jawje kykꞌuꞌja kyxolxa.
\v 10 Teyile junjun bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tajbꞌin kye txqantl, a tzeꞌnxjo toklin, a ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, tuꞌntzintla t-xi tsipiꞌn t-xtalbꞌil Dios teyile junjun atx taj te. Kybꞌinchinkuy tkyaqiljo lo tzeꞌnku jun tbꞌanil nejinel tibꞌaj aqꞌuntl, a nximin wen tiꞌj tkyaqiljo atx taj te.
\v 11 Ikytziꞌn, qa at jun at toklin tuꞌn tyolin, noqit yolin tzeꞌnkuxjo Tyol Dios. Ex qa at jun at toklin tuꞌn tajbꞌin kye txqantl, noqit tzꞌajbꞌin tukꞌa tkyaqil tipin, tzeꞌnkuxjo ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Dios, tuꞌntzintla tkyaqiljo nbꞌant, bꞌant-xitla te nimsbꞌil tbꞌi Dios, noq tuꞌn Jesucrist, a nimxit tbꞌi toj tkyaqil tipin jaꞌlin ex te jun majx. Ikyxitjo.
\s1 Qa ma tzikyꞌx quꞌn tuꞌn tpaj qnimbꞌil
\p 
\v 12 Ayiꞌy werman, at nkꞌuꞌja kyiꞌja. Mi chi jaw kaꞌylaja tuꞌn tkyaqiljo n-ikyꞌx kyiꞌja, nyakuj jun tiꞌ, a ntiꞌtaq tbꞌajil.
\v 13 Qalaꞌ, chi tzalajxa tuꞌn n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn tzeꞌnku s-ikyꞌx tuꞌn Crist, tuꞌntzintla kynojxa tukꞌa tzaljbꞌil, aj tuljo tqoptzꞌajiyil tulil.\x + \xo 4:13\xt Ro. 8:17; 1Pe. 4:1.\x*
\v 14 Ex qa ma chi ok yisoꞌn noq tuꞌn tpaj Crist, at tkyꞌiwbꞌil kyibꞌaja, noq tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan kyukꞌiy, a T-xew Dios nqoptzꞌaj wen.
\v 15 Ex qa at jun kyeꞌ n-ikyꞌx tuꞌn, me noqit nya tuꞌn tbꞌiybꞌin, mo tuꞌn telqꞌbꞌin, mo tuꞌn jun il, ex nya tuꞌn tlimoꞌn tibꞌ tiꞌjjo a ntiꞌ toklin tiꞌj, quꞌn kykyaqiljo lo n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn noq tuꞌnxjo kybꞌinchbꞌin.
\v 16 Me qa at jun n-ikyꞌx tuꞌn, noq tuꞌn tpajjo tbꞌi Crist, mina jaw txꞌixwe tuꞌn; qalaꞌ bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tnimsin tbꞌi Dios, quꞌn tuꞌn at toklin tuꞌn tok tbꞌi te nimil tiꞌj.
\v 17 Quꞌn chꞌix tjapin tqꞌijil tuꞌn qok qkyaqilx toj paꞌbꞌin twutz Dios, ex kxel xkye kyxol nimil. Ex qa il tiꞌj tuꞌn tkawin Dios kyibꞌaj nimil, ¿Yajtzila kye, a mi xi kynimin Tbꞌanil Tqanil, a tzaj tqꞌmaꞌn Dios? ¿Jaꞌtzila kchi kanile?
\p Ikytziꞌn ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios:
\v 18 Qa kuj ẍi klete kyeꞌ tzꞌaqleqe, ¿Yajtzila kye nya wenqe ex bꞌinchil ilqe?\x + \xo 4:18\xt Pr. 11:31.\x*
\p 
\v 19 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, aye n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn, tzeꞌnkuxjo tajbꞌil qMan Dios, bꞌaꞌn tuꞌn tok tilil kyuꞌn, tuꞌn tkubꞌ kybꞌinchin wen, ex tuꞌn t-xi kyoqxenin kyanmin toj tqꞌobꞌ Dios, a Chꞌiysilkye, quꞌn kukx njapin bꞌaj Tyoljo.
\c 5
\s1 Nxi tqꞌoꞌn Pegr tumil kye nimil
\p 
\v 1 Atzin jaꞌlin, kxel nqꞌoꞌn tumil kyeꞌy, ayiꞌy nejinel kyxol Ttanim Dios, quꞌn ikyx wejiꞌy, at wokliꞌn tzeꞌnkuxjo kyeꞌ. Ex o chi nlijiꞌy jniꞌ ikyꞌx tuꞌn Crist, ex knmujbꞌe wibꞌa kyukꞌiy toj kyaꞌj, aj tpon tqꞌijil tqoptzꞌajiyil Crist.
\v 2 Ayiꞌy nejinel, kykaꞌyinktzinjiꞌy nimil tiꞌj Dios, a oqxeninqe kyeꞌy, tzeꞌnku jun wen kyikꞌlel kyiꞌj trit.\x + \xo 5:2\xt Jn. 21:15-17.\x* Kybꞌinchima tukꞌa tkyaqil kyanmiꞌn, tzeꞌnkuxjo taj Dios, nya noq tuꞌn at kyaqꞌiꞌn kyiꞌj, ex nya noq tuꞌn kykanbꞌin pwaq, qalaꞌ tukꞌa tkyaqil kyajbꞌila.
\v 3 Ex mi tzꞌok kyqꞌoꞌn kyibꞌa te kyajawjo oqxeninqe kyeꞌy; qalaꞌ tok tilil kyuꞌn, tuꞌn kyoka te jun yekꞌbꞌil kywutz.
\v 4 Quꞌn tuꞌntzin aj tul Crist, ajo Tnejilxix Kyikꞌlel, ktzajil kytzyuꞌn jun oyaj tbꞌanilx, a mi bꞌaj, qalaꞌ kqoptzꞌajiyil te jun majx.\x + \xo 5:4\xt Eb. 13:20.\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ex ikyx kyejiꞌy, ayiꞌy kuꞌxinqe, kyniminqekujiꞌy at kyoklin kyibꞌaja. Ex kykyaqilxa, tuꞌn tkubꞌ kymutxsin kyibꞌa jun tukꞌa juntl, quꞌn ntqꞌmaꞌn toj Tuꞌjil Tyol Dios:
\q1 At tqꞌoj Dios kyiꞌjjo aye njaw kynimsin kyibꞌ,
\q1 me kxel tqꞌoꞌn t-xtalbꞌil kyibꞌajjo mutxin kyten.\x + \xo 5:5\xt Pr. 3:34; Sant. 4:6.\x*
\p 
\v 6 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kymutxsinku kyibꞌa twutz Dios, a nimxix tipin, tuꞌntzintla kyjaw nimsiꞌn tuꞌn, aj tpon tqꞌijil.\x + \xo 5:6\xt Mt. 23:12; Lc. 14:11; 18:14; Sant. 4:10.\x*
\v 7 Kyoqxeninxjiꞌy tkyaqiljo nbꞌaj kykꞌuꞌja tiꞌj toj tqꞌobꞌ Dios, quꞌn nqꞌaqꞌin tkꞌuꞌj Dios kyiꞌja.\x + \xo 5:7\xt Sal. 55:22; Mt. 6:25-34.\x*
\v 8 Tenxit kynabꞌla, ex kykaꞌyinktzin kyibꞌa, quꞌn a tajaw il ajqꞌoj kyiꞌja, ex nbꞌeteje kyiꞌjiliy jyol tumil tuꞌn kybꞌaja tuꞌn, ikyx tzeꞌnku jun bꞌalun ntzanin wen.
\v 9 Chi weꞌkuxixa twutz toj kynimbꞌila, quꞌn bꞌiꞌn kyuꞌn, qa kykyaqil nimil toj tkyaqil twutz txꞌotxꞌ, ikyx n-ikyꞌxjo kyuꞌn, tzeꞌnkuxjo kyeꞌ.
\v 10 Tikyꞌlinxi chꞌin yajbꞌil kyuꞌn toj jteꞌbꞌin qꞌij, axte Dios, a tzaj qꞌoꞌnte t-xtalbꞌil kyeꞌy, k-okil qꞌoꞌn kyeꞌy tzꞌaqle, jikyinxix ex kujxix, tuꞌn mi yekje, a ma tzaj txkon kyeꞌy, tuꞌn kyoka te tkꞌwal, ex tuꞌn kyxiꞌ toj tqoptzꞌajiyil kyaꞌj te jun majx noq tuꞌn Crist.
\v 11 Noqit tkyaqil tipin tukꞌa, jaꞌlin ex te jun majx.
\s1 Jun yol tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo uꞌj lo
\p 
\v 12 Ma kubꞌ ntzꞌibꞌinjiꞌy kabꞌe tal nyola lo, noq tuꞌn Silvano,\f + \fr 5:12\ft Silvano attaq juntl tbꞌi, a Silas; \xt Kybꞌi. 15:22, 40.\xt*\f* jun tbꞌanil erman toj nwutza. Noq chꞌin nyola, tuꞌn t-xi nnimsiꞌn kykꞌuꞌja, ex tuꞌn nkujsinte nyola, qa twutzxixjo a t-xtalbꞌil Dios. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, chi weꞌkuxixa toj.
\p 
\v 13 Ajo Ttanim Dios toj Babilonia, a skꞌoꞌn tuꞌn Dios ikyxjo tzeꞌnku kye, ex Marks,\x + \xo 5:13\xt Kybꞌi. 12:25; 13:13; 15:37-39; Col. 4:10; Flm. 24.\x* a nyakuj nkꞌwala, nxi kysmaꞌn qꞌolbꞌil kyeꞌy.
\v 14 Kyqꞌolbꞌink kyibꞌa kyxolxa tukꞌa tkyaqil kyanmiꞌn. Noqit a tnukꞌbꞌil Dios kyibꞌaja kykyaqila, ayiꞌy nimilqiy tiꞌj Crist.
